Опис вакансії
The international company in connection with the expansion of the staff opens the vacancy «Sales Manager» with knowledge of German or English or French!Requirements for a candidate:• Fluency in German or English or FrenchExperience in sales of financial services (must have)• Competent, well-posed speech• Sociability • Stress resistance • Punctuality • The desire to work and earnMain goals: • Consulting customers over the phone (JUST HOT customer base) • Selling products and services using arguments to potential customers • Developing strong, ongoing relationships with potential customers • Work in the CRM system; • Maintaining a customer base. Working conditions:• Salary: a fixed rate + bonuses, is always on time ;) • Schedule of work 5/2 — Monday-Friday; 10:00 — 19:00.• Office in the center of Kiev; • Tea / coffee / cookies are always in the kitchen) • Corporate events, team building and training at the expense of the company; • A young and friendly team + loyal leader) Send your CV! Or call the number:
Показати телефон Contact person: Galina
